data.description: LOOK NO FURTHER! Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home located in the desirable Fairgrounds Station neighborhood. This home has a first floor bedroom w/full hall bath. Large living room open to dining room & spacious kitchen with gorgeous backsplash and pendent lighting. Updated faucets throughout. Home overlooks pond w/fountain. Centrally located near downtown, restaurants & shopping. Enjoy sitting out on your front porch or back deck. Schedule your private showing before it's sold!
